      "from_id": "cec50b17:3",
      "to_id": "cec50b17:0",
      "content": "DONE: Two changes to src/index.ts.\n\n1. **`synapse update [path]` command** (line 226):\n   - New Commander command added between `init` and `run`\n   - Calls `synapseInit(resolve(targetPath ?? '.'), true)` (update=true path)\n   - `--update` / `-u` flag on `init` is kept for backwards compatibility\n\n2. **Browser open on `synapse start`** (lines 365-368):\n   - `startDashboard` return value captured as `actualPort`\n   - Cross-platform opener: `open` (macOS) / `start` (Windows) / `xdg-open` (Linux)\n   - Uses `exec()` (non-blocking, fire-and-forget) — not `execSync`\n   - Added `exec` to the `child_process` import on line 7\n\nBuild: `tsc` passes clean.",
